  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U Hispaniji, broj 20 je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinte</span>.</p>\n<p>Kada generišete brojeve od 21 do 29, reči se malo menjaju. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinte</span> menja se u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinti-</span> (uklanja se poslednji deo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>), zatim se spaja sa sledećim brojem. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinti</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">dos</span> (mbili) = <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veintidós</span> (22)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinti</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">cinco</span> (pet) = <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veinticinco</span> (25)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinti</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ocho</span> (nane) = <span class=\"highlighted-text\">veintiocho</span> (28)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
  "instructions": "<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>",
  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Veinticinco años</span> - Dvadeset pet godina.</p>\n</section>",
